DATA LICENSES

This software uses data from external sources with the following licenses:

1. IPC (Integrated Food Security Phase Classification) Data
   Source: Famine Early Warning Systems Network (FEWSNET)
   URL: https://fews.net/fews-data/335
   License: FEWSNET Terms of Use
   Attribution: Famine Early Warning Systems Network (FEWSNET). (2024).
                Integrated Food Security Phase Classification (IPC) data.

2. GDELT (Global Database of Events, Language, and Tone) Data
   Source: The GDELT Project
   URL: https://www.gdeltproject.org/
   License: Creative Commons Attribution 4.0 International (CC BY 4.0)
   Attribution: Leetaru, K., & Schrodt, P. A. (2013). GDELT: Global data on
                events, location and tone. ISA Annual Convention.

3. GADM (Database of Global Administrative Areas)
   Source: GADM
   URL: https://gadm.org/
   License: Free for academic use
   Attribution: GADM. (2024). Database of Global Administrative Areas, version 4.1.

4. Natural Earth
   Source: Natural Earth
   URL: https://www.naturalearthdata.com/
   License: Public Domain
   Attribution: Natural Earth. Free vector and raster map data.

